{"tid":289413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】九龍塘驚現「TNT」詐彈","createTime":"2017-06-19T03:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T19:57:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e73255259523c84177820319974153e7ffaffd29","tid":289413,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060698&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060698%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=53606c44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060698%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170619&h=c6ae5fc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060698&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170619</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n九龍塘驚現「TNT」詐彈<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全球恐襲浪潮不斷，加上國家主席習近平料將來港出席回歸20周年慶典，九龍塘上周四驚現印有「TNT」、「HIGH EXPLOSIVE」字樣的懷疑炸彈裝置，警方大為緊張，爆炸品處理課人員利用拆彈機械人引爆，發現該物件並無炸藥成份，這是半月內第二宗街頭放懷疑炸彈案件。由於正值敏感時刻，警方追緝放彈者及其動機，不排除有人試圖測試警方應變能力。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=zGjnhggtEuWaQdY2yEmPV54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b2be466d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"63359f219be754ceb77401aa9167690a8585d4ee","tid":289413,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57c08312466a0b0ccd248e9994b6792c1540ffcc","tid":289413,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-